Hugosave is a digital companion empowering any generation to spend, save, and invest confidently, effortlessly and sustainably through an inclusive and easy-to-understand wealthcare journey.

About Hugosave's Features >>>

Open your Hugosave account in less than 60 seconds; no ID documents needed to get started:
- Monies are safeguarded within DBS Bank; 
- Load money from any bank account of your choice within Singapore;
- Transfer money to your family and friends.

The Hugo Visa Platinum Debit Card: 
- The first ‘Digital First’’ Visa Platinum Debit Card in Singapore from a fintech;
- Numberless card designed to keep your transactions super safe;
- Manage your card from within the app
- View card details & PIN, instantly lock & unlock the card or request a replacement if lost or stolen;
- Use your Hugosave Card for everyday spends and enjoy Visa Platinum offers on leading merchants;
- Use your Hugosave Card worldwide with NO additional forex charges. 

Roundups: Turn spare change into real gold! 
- Your card transactions will be rounded up to the nearest dollar and the excess saved;
- Each week, your Roundups are automatically invested into real physical gold for growth!

Gold Vault: Include gold as part of a healthy savings & investment plan! 
- Buy and sell gold from as low as SGD0.01; 
- Set a monthly schedule to automatically grow your investment in gold;
- See live gold prices to know what your investment is worth at any moment; 
- Real physical gold allocated to you and held on your behalf in an accredited LBMA (London Bullion Market Association) vault;
- Insured by Lloyd's of London, your gold is safe and secure.

Money Pots: Smartest Piggy banks ever!
- Set financial goals and track your progress easily;
- Plan and save for as many goals as you wish such as, a new smartwatch, a staycation, your honeymoon etc.!
- Set an automated monthly savings schedule to invest diligently.

Trivia:  The name Hugo is derived from the Mandarin word Hu (互) which means 'Mutual' and the English word Go which signifies 'Progress'. This spirit of mutual growth and prosperity is the driving force behind Hugo.

Atlas Consolidated Pte. Ltd is the owner of the Hugosave brand, an authorised card distributor and programme manager of Payrnet Pte. Ltd (UEN 201913150C), currently exempted by the Monetary Authority of Singapore pursuant to the Payment Services (Exemption for Specified Period) Regulations 2019, incorporated in Singapore whose registered address is 52 Craig Road, Singapore 089690. Atlas is regulated as a Major Payment Institution (MPI) by the Monetary Authority of Singapore (MAS) under the Payment Services Act (No. 2 of 2019).

As a dynamic bank in digital transformation, Vietcombank constantly researches and develops to launch new digital products, helping Vietcombank’s customers to be simpler, more stylish and more satisfied when dealing with us, it makes life more meaningful when saving time for transactions, enjoying meaningful time with family and relatives.

VCB Digibank is built on the integration of transaction platforms on Internet Banking and Mobile Banking, helping to bring seamless, unified experience to customers on electronic media such as computers (PC/Laptop) and mobile devices (mobile/tablets). VCB Digibank service has 01 version on mobile application - VCB Digibank application, and 01 version on web browser in menu VCB Digibank on Vietcombank’s official website: www.vietcombank.com.vn

 
Along with the web browser, VCB Digibank's application aims to meet all basic financial transactions and other life needs of customers at anytime, anywhere, simply and quickly as:
-	Inquiry information of payment account, saving account, loan account, card;
-	Transfer within VCB, quick transfer 24/7, transfer outside VCB;
-	Online savings;
-	Schedule transfer, future transfer;
-	Pay for most utility bills;
-	Auto bill payments;
-	Mobile topup;
-	QR Code payment;
-	Online shopping, hotel booking, air ticket booking,….
-	Verify security transactions through Smart OTP with limit up to 3 billion VND / transaction for priority customers and 01 billion VND / transaction for normal customers.
-	Utility to receive OTT Alert notification message right on the application when account fluctuations, card spending;
-	And many other attractive digital utilities
In addition, VCB Digibank application creates a breakthrough in customer’s experience:

-	 The design style of "Dark Mode" - dark background mode - is a remarkable highlight in the design of VCB Digibank. Dark Mode is currently a prominent trend on software and operating systems today, based on the benefits of using dark background mode, especially for user health and durability of the device; and
-	Customers can easily personalize with a wide selection of personality wallpapers for VCB Digibank on their favorite applications and web browsers.
